Core Business Components:

1. Daily Mission System (Importance: 95)
- Generates exactly 5 random questions per daily mission
- Enforces single active mission per user per day
- Maintains mission states: NOT_STARTED, IN_PROGRESS, COMPLETE, ARCHIVED
- Automatically archives incomplete missions at daily reset

